OL,6,FIt's been 10 years since the landmark
OL,7,Freport looking at deaths caused by
OL,8,Fasthma was published.
OL,10,FSusan Turner, Elisha's mother, said
OL,11,Fshe "went numb" when she was told to
OL,12,Fprepare for Elisha's death in hospital
OL,13,Fafter her condition deteriorated.
OL,15,FShe said: "I just thought all this
OL,16,Ftime we've done everything we can and
OL,17,Fthis one thing has put her here and we
OL,18,Fmight lose her.
