OL,3,CMum 'went numb' as daughter's severe
OL,4,Casthma left her fighting for breath
OL,6,F"It was scary and I just felt numb and
OL,7,FI don't know why, I can't really
OL,8,Fexplain but it was almost like I felt
OL,9,Fshe'd come to the end."
OL,11,FElisha has endured a lifetime of being
OL,12,Fforced to miss out on big events but
OL,13,Fis determined to not let her illness
OL,14,Fget the better of her.
OL,16,FShe's recently engaged and won the
OL,17,FMiss Elegance of the World pageant in
OL,18,FFlorida.
